summary: So I have run a small group at work, using art as a positive outlet for some children (aged 9/10) with behavioural issues and I...
body:
So I have run a small group at work, using art as a positive outlet for some children (aged 9/10) with behavioural issues and I let them use ipads as means to find references. Anyway, it went something like this:

Child A: Urghhhh Miss! Someone’s drawn Venom kissing Spiderman!!

Me: *sweats*

Child B: So!? There’s nothing wrong with being gay.

Child A: I know that but it’s venom and with those teeth he could eat his face!

I mean…

summary: He looked at me, started to get angry as I ran faster out of the door - “I’m gonna break your hands Loki !!” For god Norn sake,...
title: He looked at me, started to get angry as I ran faster out of the door - “I’m gonna break your hands Loki !!” For god Norn sake, Fandral is my only savior now.
body:
(Warning: Situations and Loki’s emotions do not fit with the original Marvel’s movie or plot, so if you’re the person who cares about the original plot more than fanfic character’s sentiments then don’t read it, I won’t be responsible for this. And for god Norn sake my grammar sucks.)

Frigga understand her adopted child. Loki is a good boy, and a beautiful prince. Although, he can’t be the king of Asgard, because of his origins that he shall not know, and the first born will always inherit their father’s throne. Loki, sometimes let his childish side to be revealed, and sometimes let out his naughty side.

Because, sometimes, we’ll see a Loki runs from his brother’s room with a brush on his hand. We would never know what it was if Thor didn’t run after him, screaming. He looks at Loki, starts to get angry as Loki runs faster out of the door. “I’m gonna break your hands Loki !!” For god Norn sake, Fandral is Loki’s only savior now. 

Speaking of Fandral, we will find out about this guy.

Fandral the Dashing, what a great name. He is seen as a member of Warrior Three and Lady Sif, friends of Thor. To know better, Fandral is the warrior that owns a beautiful blonde hair, the sweet sweet honey eyes-colored with the beard which makes him looks like a prince more than Thor. With his rapier sword and his fantastic charming look, no one can tell he is a warrior, not a prince. 

And somehow, Loki is connected to that badass.

Fandral is seen as Loki’s groom, always be clingy around Loki all day, all night. But a thing which most people don’t know, is Fandral isn’t the kind of groom that acting like a fool for the prince of Asgard, he is seen like Loki’s brother, strangely. Like, Fandral could be with Loki all day, take care for Loki any time he wants or he needs, but acts like he’s Loki’s brother. Even Thor doesn’t have those actions. 

So, it could likely to be called as: Fandral is Loki’s savior.

“What’s the matter my prince ?” Fandral said in a sweet, serviceable voice that could melt every girl’s heart.

Since he saw Loki was running out of Thor’s room with a panicking face, he started to be worried.

“Save me, even if I’m wrong or right, you’re my only savior, protect me at any cost !!” Loki yells, pulls Fandral to another room. At a same time, Thor passes by without looking into the room that holds a person he is looking for. After seeing Loki’s brother’s face, Fandral smartly figure out the situation. 

A-ha, this little naughty prince.. “Don’t worry my prince, I’ll protect you all life !” Fandral said, proudly. And Loki feels relieved too. He smiles shyly when he notices he’s holding Fandral’s hand.

And that’s why Fandral could smile so bright like that.

“Could I tell that you’re sick now, my prince ?” said Fandral looking at Loki’s eyes deeply and impassioned, rubbing his thumb to his prince’s hand. Feeling warm and beloved, is what Loki is taking now.

Loki detects that his cheeks are getting hotter too. “N-No, I am- not ! I-I just..” The little prince tries his best to act normal and strict, and he doesn’t even know that way failed. Fandral chuckles at the cuteness of his prince, kisses on Loki’s cheek with caressing slightly on the cheek. 

That moment Loki thinks he was going to explode. 

“Then good, I’m good if you’re good too, my prince !” he said. 

The atmosphere will be more awkward if Thor doesn’t plan to show up behind the two of them. He appears to be really really really stupid, with ink on his face, and some parts of his hair are tightening. Looks really alike a failed surgery doll, and Loki doesn’t know which to react, laugh or scared. 

Fandral tries not to laugh hardly, cover Loki by his cape, his charming face gradually turning into an emotion that is hard to say.

“We shall run, my prince.” He whispers, then pulls Loki out of the room, run insanely from a awakening monster after a thousand years sleeping.

And, they were safe. At least for Loki. Fandral was being beaten up all that afternoon.

So we can tell, Loki has a great and charming savior, Fandral. Such a wonderful fortune, Loki loves it.

yeah, i said i’ll make fanfics based on these fanarts haha

and screw my terrible grammar and typos lol
